{"word":"G160 - αἰφνίδιος - aiphnídios - aheef-nid'-ee-os - Sudden","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">αἰφνίδιος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">aiphnídios</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">aheef-nid'-ee-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Sudden</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"நினையாத, சடிதியாய் - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"unexpected, sudden, unforeseen"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G5316 - φαίνω - phaínō - fah'-ee-no/5316\">G5316</a> (compare <a href=\"#/G1810 - ἐξαίφνης - exaíphnēs - ex-ah'-eef-nace/1810\">G1810</a>), (meaning <i>non apparent</i>); <i>unexpected</i>, that is, (adverbially) <i>suddenly:</i> - sudden, unawares.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}